    <div class="hc-eyebrow">The tool</div>
    <h2 class="hc-h2">Where you are decides</h2>
    <p class="hc-lead hc-playground-sub">Raising cash is selling &mdash; converting part of one stack into its other form, not setting money aside from it. The full cycle &mdash; sell, wait, rebuy &mdash; is the <strong>round trip</strong>, and where in the <a href="/the-power-law">Power Law channel</a> you run it decides whether it ends in more bitcoin or less. Set the split and a tax rate, then drag the two sliders below &mdash; where you sell, and where you rebuy &mdash; and the verdict follows from it.</p>

