      <div class="hc-alarm" id="hcAlarm" hidden>
        <span class="hc-alarm-tag">Past 80%, this is an exit</span>
        <p>Past 80% this stops being a buffer and starts being an exit. Worth remembering before you go further: a stack this hedged has already given up most of its drawdown risk &mdash; and most of its upside. Selling this much realizes the tax bill in one season. And the Power Law is a floor observed, not a ceiling promised: if bitcoin ever breaks it upward into an S-curve, the bitcoin you sold is what misses it. The default posture of this site is HODL; the opportunity here is a conservative trim, not a departure.</p>
