    <div class="hc-prose">
      <p><a href="/disciplined-rebalancing">Disciplined Rebalancing</a> states the protocol &mdash; trim strength, rebuy weakness, by zone. This page prices it: what the trim costs after tax, where in the channel it has historically paid, and how long the round trip took. Same discipline, with the work shown.</p>
